list.abstract: Instance（英[ˈɪnstəns]，美[ˈɪnstəns]），英语单词，作名词用，为例子；事例；具体事件。作动词用，为以…为例。短语搭配有for instance（例如），例句为“For instance, they may drop difficult coursework.（例如，他们可能会放弃困难的课程。）” Instance名词类近义词有situation、case、circumstance等，instances是Instance的复数以及第三人称单数形式。

yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是"打个比方"。什么意思？

yingyinNormal.en: Like this desk, for instance. It could be something special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像这张桌子，它可以变得很特别。

yingyinNormal.en: In this one and only instance, I am glad to hear it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是绝无仅有的一次。我很高兴听你这么说。

yingyinNormal.en: And in every instance, you did so on you own volition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但每一次，都是你自己的决定。

yingyinNormal.en: For instance, let me show you another move. The dramatic exit. What's that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 打个比方，我来教你另一招华丽退场，那是啥？

yingyinNormal.en: For instance, there's a particle called a squark, which could prove supersymmetry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如说，有个粒子叫超对称性夸克，它能证明超对称性。

yingyinNormal.en: You go to your closet and you select, I don't know, that lumpy blue sweater, for instance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你去自己的衣橱选择，我不知道，比如你那松垮的蓝色绒线衫。

yingyinNormal.en: Has anyone around you? For instance, your father? He was scared. He wasn't thinking right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你身边的人有过质疑吗？比如说你父亲？他很害怕，他的思绪不清晰。

yingyinNormal.en: When learning about another person's abilities and competencies, for instance, this bias flips.
yingyinNormal.zh: 举例来说这偏见就完全不相同。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, for instance. Let's say, Janice is coming back from a trip and she gives you two options.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，比如说，珍妮丝旅行回来，她给你两种选择。

yingyinNormal.en: For instance, if we were talking about a crime, then confessing to the authorities would prove the intentions of our heart.
yingyinNormal.zh: 假如你犯了刑事罪，跟当局坦白，就能表明悔改之心。

yingyinNormal.en: Sir William Lucas, for instance, is a very agreeable man. And a good deal less self-important than some people half his rank.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如威廉·卢卡斯爵士就是位很和蔼的人。跟他同一爵位的某些人比起来，他是那么温雅的好人。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, well, that's okay then. But, okay my towels for instance. I come in to the bathroom here and my towel is not on the floor where keep it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就没关系，像我的浴巾，我走进浴室，我的浴巾却不在地板上。

yingyinNormal.en: Can I ask you a question? Sure. When did you first become so advanced? So I became advanced? Well, I mean for instance when did you start to read.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可以问你一个问题吗？当然。你从什么时候开始变得这么知识渊博的？所以我是"变得"知识渊博的吗？不，我是说比如你什么时候开始阅读的。

yingyinNormal.en: So I think, in that instance, I was just learning to fight To constantly live and play for god. And when I do that, I'll be able to walk on water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以在那件事上我只是学着去奋斗，去为了神而生活和打球，如果我做到这些，我就能完成看似不可能的事情

yingyinNormal.zh: 比如？首先想到的就是隔离你大脑里负责存储记忆的部分，然后用激光切掉它。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my goodness. Where do I begin? For instance, My laptop contained four out of the five gedanken experiments necessary for a cogent restatement of the quantum measurement problem.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天呐，多得去了，比如说，我笔记本电脑里有五种思维实验，其中四种都是关于量子测量课题的强有力的重述。

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: For <highlight>instance</highlight>, having spent many generations hunting the fat marine mammals of the Arctic, the Eskimos of Greenland have developed certain genetic adaptations.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，格陵兰岛的爱斯基摩人历经数代狩猎北极地区肥胖的海洋哺乳动物，他们已经进化出某些遗传适应性。

examination_example.sentence: Take, for <highlight>instance</highlight>, the age at which people make commitments such as buying a house, getting married, having children, or starting a career. These are all fundamental commitments that are now occurring later in life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 就拿人们履行买房、结婚、生育、或步入职场的责任的年龄为例。如今都在推迟履行这些基本责任。

examination_example.sentence: Carpets, for <highlight>instance</highlight>, seem to be slightly better places to drop your food than wood or tile.

examination_example.sentence: For <highlight>instance</highlight>, if the host casually acknowledges that there is a camera in the room by telling a story about it, that may be enough to provide an opening for a guest to say if they are uncomfortable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，如果主人通过讲述一个关于摄像头的故事随意地承认房间里有一个摄像头，这可能足以让客人说出他们是否感到不舒服。

examination_example.sentence: Should you tell your friends, for <highlight>instance</highlight>, that they're being recorded while you all watch the big game together?
